  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the fideo and cook for 2-3 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the spicy sauce, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, until the fideo is coated in the spice mixture.",
    "Add the scrambled eggs and cook until they are set.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and sugar (if using)."
